label: ItemAvailability
comment: A list of possible product availability options.

enumerationMembers.label: BackOrder
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is available on back order.

enumerationMembers.label: Discontinued
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item has been discontinued.

enumerationMembers.label: InStock
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is in stock.

enumerationMembers.label: InStoreOnly
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is available only at physical locations.

enumerationMembers.label: LimitedAvailability
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item has limited availability.

enumerationMembers.label: MadeToOrder
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is made to order (custom made).

enumerationMembers.label: OnlineOnly
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is available only online.

enumerationMembers.label: OutOfStock
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is out of stock.

enumerationMembers.label: PreOrder
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is available for pre-order.

enumerationMembers.label: PreSale
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is available for ordering and delivery before general availability.

enumerationMembers.label: Reserved
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item is reserved and therefore not available.

enumerationMembers.label: SoldOut
enumerationMembers.comment: Indicates that the item has sold out.
